I"†<h2 class="fs-9" id="general-definition-of-an-atomic-nft">General definition of an atomic NFT</h2>

<p>Atomic NFT is a standard for Non Fungible Tokens (NFTs) on Koii.</p>

<p>Anyone can utilize the Atomic NFT standard to tokenize and create digital assets and buy, sell &amp; auction assets utilizing the marketplace.</p>

<p>Alongside its smart contract creation platform Atomic Market. Atomic Market is a shared liquidity NFT market smart contract that is used by multiple websites to try and provide users the best possible experience. Shared liquidity means that everything which is listed on one market also shows on all other markets.</p>
